      "title": "Suddenly reduced cooking gas prices",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Accordingly, the price of 12.5 kg LPG gas cylinder has been reduced by 1050 rupees. Accordingly, the new price is Rs.5800."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
